{
  "stem": "15115.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was the superintendent of the building in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I start crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The superintendent says, what's happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What's happened, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In Greek, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I told him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He says, don't worry, he says.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He took my hat, put it over the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The bed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Gave me a glass of water, and he says, go into bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I got into bed, and he kept me there until about 12:00.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then he says, OK, now we'll take you home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He took me home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was a Greek Gentile.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He took me home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My mother, poor mother, was waiting, crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Where am I?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was so late.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So as soon as I got home, I went to the mezuzah, you know, and I prayed to God, thank God that I'm at my house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My mother says, what happened to you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Told her the story and then I almost came in tears, but I was very fortunate I made it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So that was the only thing that had happened to me during the occupation that my life was at stake, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Everything else was normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And like everybody else suffered, I suffered, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And that's why-- What other laws were in place?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They made you wear the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The star.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The curfews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's about it, but there was no Jewish business anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the Jewish business was already gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of the Jewish businesses-- there were a couple big businesses which were Gentile and Jews, partners.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They still, when they went back after the war, they got it back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't that bad, the Greeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the Germans, they had a system.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had a system, and they wouldn't-- they wouldn't rush nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was done because they had done this before.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
